Romulus is the worlds tallest living donkey, as certified by the Guinness World Records. 12 years old and has been measured at 17 hands 68 inches, 173 cm from hooves to withers, two inches taller than the former tallest donkey, Oklahoma Sam. Romulus weighs about,1 1,300 pounds 590 kg. He is owned by Phil and Cara Barker Yellott of Adrian, Michigan.
